ceration would be more beneficial.<br><br>Most of the Mage AA skills did not impress me, and I haven't had any interest in pouring more time into getting them... I've been playing my Rogue. :) <p><h6><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=55098>Rulan Jiggamental</a><BR>Arch Mage of <a href=http://www.warzonedirect.com/DO/MainDO.html>Veneration</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uwolandgrauensturm.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Woland Grauensturm</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/14/02 8:04:01 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Wanted opinion of the Class ability Pet Hold.....</span><hr size=1> <br>AEs eat the pets anyway. At least my necro pets (including the 59 one). Verant need to come up with a viable solution to make pets a bit more useful when fighting mobs with damage AE's. <br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ucobeeblazesummoner.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Cobee Blazesummoner</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/14/02 8:06:25 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Wanted opinion of the Class ability Pet Hold.....</span><hr size=1> Hmm...<br><br>I think any decent mag/nec could keep a pet under control 